description: Demolition of existing buildings and erection of two 3-, 4- & 5-storey blocks totalling 143 dwellings, comprising 21 x one-bedroom flats, 23 x two-bedroom flats, 31 x three-bedroom flats, 11 x four-bedroom maisonettes, 2 x five-bedroom maisonettes (affordable) and 12 x one-bedroom flats & 43 x two-bedroom flats (private housing), with 26 surface and 80 basement car-parking spaces, amenity space, children's play area and bin stores (as amended by plans received 04/03/2010 and 15/03/2010) and subject to a Deed of Agreement dated 18 March 2010 under Section 106 of the Town and Country Planning Act 1990, as amended.
